data.title: Moe and the Big Exit (Video Game)
authors: Contributors to PBS Kids Fanon Wiki
data.meta_description: Moe and the Big Exit is an adventure game developed by THQ and Big Idea Interactive for Sega Mega Drive/Sega Genesis, SNES, Nintendo GameCube, PlayStation 2, XBOX, Sega DreamCast, Sega Saturn, PlayStation, and Nintendo 64.
